                    "body": "Please comment to the correct issue.\n\nAs said before, when the cache should not be used within Zend_Locale then disable the cache usage.\n\nSee:\nhttp:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.locale.html#zend.locale.cache\n\nQuote:\n\"Sometimes it is wished to prevent that a cache is set, even if this degrades performance. In this case the static disableCache(true) method should be used. It does not only disable the actual set cache, without erasing it, but also prevents that a cache is automatically generated when no cache is set.\"",
